hing and sorting. &nbsp;You can search, filter, and sort in any order, and the final result will obey all three.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 8pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: ''Trebuchet MS''; color: #3d85c6; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">4.7.1 Clearing Filters</span></h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">To remove all of the filters at once and see the full, unfiltered list, click the clear filters button</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/9Uv1xqyjEl4qMmou1dtXoizAlVEpR6-Dlc30LqJXEJygfFUGCmLkztd91CfIlKPxWhE57bGMlS6eHNEtRG-kXZTlwIG8POxr-kquYf0EaFtg7UyxfuZZoE693yGIDlaQBw" alt="" width="29px;" height="29px;" /></span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">which can be found in the top right corner of the Filters section.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0),
(11, '4. Workflows  -  4.8 Sorting ideas', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-c44a3040-e8af-6b15-9fbf-fedb581c965c" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You may be interested in seeing your ideas sorted in a certain way, to do so, use the Sorting section on the Search page.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/7qeFjGqcA2vYA_up7ebSn56Fe6B9X_MsAwyOp2hzpj6UV5glToRwqqqi80v3S1ArbsWnpkH16d7yUe1sFyUgKjAXIoImvoBGSKAh6_DYN1mg6oqxUyqD5tFfpyfHegGD-w" alt="" width="259px;" height="112px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 1: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">To search for an idea, click the </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Search</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> button located on the navbar.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/byshM0P40taVfn_oUMo__sdujY31bkkKf8o0tODJOLHaspdMtNcy-7d7p9ztKlFpbSPsHxFtTM5W126wsfdo1YA784Tj_L_RVOAqosdCeUA3yKG68gq-KI36RlKMUrxb1A" alt="" width="81px;" height="51px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 2: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Select a value to sort by. These values include Unsorted, Name, Community Partner, Idea created, Idea last updated, Project start date, and Project end date.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: 